# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Vaulter AI Property Intelligence System
# Environment Variables — Example File
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# SETUP INSTRUCTIONS:
#   1. Copy this file to your confidentials/ folder
#   2. Rename it to .env (remove the .example)
#   3. Fill in your actual values below
#   4. NEVER commit the real .env to GitHub
#
# File location:
#   Windows : C:\Users\YashuLanki\Vaulter AI\confidentials\.env
#   Mac     : <project_root>/confidentials/.env
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════


# ── Anthropic / Claude API ────────────────────────────────────────
# Get this from: https://console.anthropic.com → API Keys
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-your-key-here


# ── Microsoft Outlook / Graph API ────────────────────────────────
# Get these from: portal.azure.com → App registrations. One shared app
# registration (CLIENT_ID/TENANT_ID) works for the whole team -- each
# person still signs in individually with their own Microsoft account.
OUTLOOK_CLIENT_ID=your-application-id-here
OUTLOOK_TENANT_ID=your-directory-tenant-id-here


# ── Google Places API Key ─────────────────────────────────────────
# Used by the proximity/nearby-places search tools.
GOOGLE_PLACES_API_KEY=your-google-places-key-here


# ── Google Maps Platform Key ──────────────────────────────────────
# Used by the CoStar screening pipeline's Phase 4 ground-truth checks
# (elevation, roads, satellite/street view, distance to market, etc.).
# Optional -- if unset, Phase 4 still runs, just skips this enrichment.
GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=your-google-maps-key-here


# ── Shared Team Folder (optional) ─────────────────────────────────
# Only needed if your OneDrive folder isn't named/located at the
# auto-detected default (see config.py's _detect_shared_dir). Points at
# the shared folder where CoStar screening results are saved so the
# whole team benefits from a single screening run instead of everyone
# re-paying for the same file.
# VAULTER_SHARED_DIR=C:\Users\YourName\OneDrive - Vaulter LLC\Vaulter AI Shared


# ── Scheduled Web/Property Scraping (optional) ────────────────────
# Web and property-intelligence scraping hit the same public pages no
# matter whose machine runs them -- there's no benefit to every staff
# member's instance doing it independently. Leave this UNSET (or "true")
# on one designated team machine, and set it to "false" here on every
# other machine so only that one machine does the scraping. Email is
# never affected by this -- it's always per-person.
# RUN_SCHEDULED_SCRAPING=false
